name: Acadian Timber Corp.
longDescription: Acadian Timber Corp is a Canada-based supplier of primary forest products in Eastern Canada and the Northeastern United States. The company's operating segments include NB Timberlands and Maine Timberlands. It generates maximum revenue from the NB Timberlands segment. The company's product includes softwood and hardwood sawlogs, pulpwood and biomass by-products.
